channel.title: DubScape | Old Skool meets New School | 317[PI] - Something Unique
channel.description:
[center]
[size=24pt]Website now 100% forum almost complete! However we b releasin both tonight!![/size]
[b]Website: [/b] [url=http://dubscape.no-ip.org]Click Here![/url]
[b]Forums: [/b] [url=http://dubscape.no-ip.org/forum]Click Here![/url]
[b][size=18pt]Incase one of the hyperlinks isn't working here is the URL: http://dubscape.no-ip.org yes im using no-ip for the site until i can afford a domain![/size]
Permission from JME. [/b]
[size=14pt]Current Server State: Alpha[/size] [/center] -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [center] [b][shadow=red,right][size=18pt]Important News:[/size][/shadow] [b] I've just ordered a VPS should be setup soon. Beta Soon? -.^ ?[/b][/center]
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Intro:[/b] Welcome to the world of DubScape. In this server my partner and I (tyb97) Have tried creating something unique. Whats the #1 problem with servers these days? Servers overloaded with Customs and The same PI remakes. The whole purpose of RSPS were to make rs easier. All of us loved rs at one point and time, why did we quit? It was bullshit and too difficult. However the modern day servers have become to easy. What have we done/plan to do on Dubscape? Below you will find a mixture of list, pictures, and videos.
[b]Server Info: [/b]PI | Revision: 317 | Source: Rune - Mtp
[b]Max Players Held: [/b]Not Hosting Don't Plan on it For A Month or So.
[b]Team: [/b]Me (eballer48) | Tyler (Tyb97)
[center][b][u]Forums[/u] | [u]Website[/b] [size=6pt][i]Tyler and I Haven't Decided to Release The Website / Forums But When We Do We Will Make Sure To Have Permission From A Mod.[/i][/size][/center]
[center][b][size=24pt]Goals[/size] [b] |- Red - Not Started -| |- Orange - In-Progress -| |- Green - Completed -| |- Blue - Stalled -|
Player Owned Shops / Houses - 0% Correct Teleports / Teletabs (Each one has 5 uses) - 100% Unique Ways Of Travel (Teletabs, Magic Books, Boats, Canoes, Shortcuts, Fairy Rings) - 60% (Need to finish Boats/Canoes Havent Started on Fairy Rings Yet) All Working Skills (Including Hunter, Dung, Con) Each At Least 80% Rs Like - 50% Decently Stable PI - 75% (Thanks to Imsuperman05) 100% Working RS Like Mini-games Including Godwars, CW, Etc Recreating Major RS City's (All f2p and some P2p) Medium EXP Rates! Takes About 1 Day (8-10 Hrs) to get 99 In A Skill - 40% Recreating All f2p Quest and a few p2p Quest Creating A Few Custom Quest Balanced Economy, PKing, and Skilling Server - 30% Tutorial Island - 100% Secret Will Release When Is At 50% - 0%
[center][b][size=24pt]Media[/size]
[b]Dungeoneering Video:[/b] [i]Dung has changed (improved since this video | added so npcs dont respawn + more)[/i] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OOZl6g6HwxM[/youtube]
[b]Al-Kharid Gate[/b] [IMG]http://i1132.photobucket.com/albums/m575/BlahBerrys/whatyouradding.png[/img]
[b]Canoes[/b] [i]Busy ATM Will Add Pics Later or Tomorrow...[/i]
[b]Boats - 50%[/b] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8NKHsMOAVAY[/youtube]
[b]Gnome Gliders[/b] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AkW4x7-pciw[/youtube]
[b]Shortcuts[/b] [i]Busy ATM Will Add Pics Later or Tomorrow...[/i]
[b]TuT Island[/b] [i]Busy ATM Will Add Pics Later or Tomorrow...[/i]
[b]Citys[/b]
[b]Skills[/b]
[i]FM[/i] [IMG]http://i1132.photobucket.com/albums/m575/BlahBerrys/fm.jpg[/img] [i]More Soon...[/i]
[b]Basic Requirements[/b] [i]Teleporting...] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=78aue3-TGLQ[/youtube]
[b][i][size=14pt]I Know I Haven't Posted Much Media But I Havent Taken Alot of Screenys And I CBA To Do Any Right Now... None The Less Please Be Patient![/size][/i][/b]
[b][size=12pt][u]Eric's Daily Log[/u][/size][/b] [i]Title is deceiving, I dont update this dialog however I try.[/i]
[b][10/1/2011][/b] Wow, added a dick load today, Gnome Gliders done, Boats 50-70%, Added some requirements and doing website/forums tonight. Pce.
[b][9/28/2011][/b] Imsuperman05 Gave me his firemaking and adding MAJOR stability (fixed alot of memleaks), finished canoe stations in lumby and Barb village. Adding Pic soon.
[b][9/26/2011][/b] Created Dev thread, and finished canoes in Lumby and the one next to Barb Village - Adding Pics Soon.
[size=16pt][center]Below Tyler has reserved a spot. There he will post his own update of the server. Please post criticism and suggestions![/center]
